name: Official iOS 14 (Beta) Design Templates + UI Elements + Guides
description:
Apple Design Resources for iOS include comprehensive UI resources that depict the full range of controls, views, and glyphs available to developers using the iOS SDK. These resources help you design apps that match the iOS design language. Icon and glyph production files are preconfigured to automate asset production using Figma. Color swatches, dynamic type tables, and fonts are also included. 

Directly from https://developer.apple.com/design/resources/
